00:35:42.080 --> 00:35:43.600
Hindi mo man lang nirerespeto.

00:35:43.800 --> 00:35:45.080
Nagsasagwan ako ngayon lang.

00:35:45.680 --> 00:35:45.920
Pero wala ka na ngayon.

00:35:45.920 --> 00:35:46.920
O paano kaya natin magagawa

00:35:46.920 --> 00:35:47.760
mauna ka sa loob?

00:35:47.920 --> 00:35:48.800
Bukod pa rito,

00:35:48.880 --> 00:35:50.520
bakit kailangan may karera ang lahat?

00:35:52.160 --> 00:35:53.600
Wala man lang finish line.

00:35:55.000 --> 00:35:56.640
Bakit ba tayo patuloy na naliligaw sa ganoong paraan?

00:35:57.680 --> 00:35:59.640
Kaibigan, maling direksyon.

00:35:59.640 --> 00:36:00.360
Sa ganoong paraan.

00:36:00.360 --> 00:36:01.000
Alam ko.

00:36:01.000 --> 00:36:02.680
Sabi ni Li Daoqi, hanapin mo ang baluktot na puno.

00:36:02.680 --> 00:36:03.680
Iyon ang katapusan.

00:36:04.600 --> 00:36:06.240
Ngunit bawat puno sa daan

00:36:06.480 --> 00:36:07.920
ay baluktot.

00:36:07.920 --> 00:36:08.440
Nagkaroon

00:36:08.440 --> 00:36:10.120
isang maliit na tinidor kanina,

00:36:10.120 --> 00:36:11.240
nagkamali tayo ng liko.

00:36:11.240 --> 00:36:12.960
Dapat sana ay lumiko tayo sa kaliwa.

00:36:14.360 --> 00:36:15.960
Ngayon tingnan mo kami.

00:36:16.520 --> 00:36:17.480
Nahuhuli na tayo.

00:36:22.320 --> 00:36:23.160
Nagsasagwan ako sa unahan,

00:36:23.160 --> 00:36:24.440
at nangingisda ka lang?

00:36:24.440 --> 00:36:25.680
Kaya mo 'yan.

00:36:25.760 --> 00:36:27.000
Ikaw ang pinakamahusay, mahal.

00:36:30.920 --> 00:36:31.880
May dala ako.

00:36:32.240 --> 00:36:33.040
- Ano?
- Parang sanga.

00:36:36.640 --> 00:36:37.120
Bakit...

00:36:37.120 --> 00:36:38.080
Saan ito napunta?

00:36:38.680 --> 00:36:40.000
Bakit umiikot ang ating bangka?

00:36:42.520 --> 00:36:43.240
Naghahabol na sila!

00:36:43.240 --> 00:36:44.160
Bilisan mo, bilisan mo!

00:36:44.440 --> 00:36:45.280
Nasaan sila?

00:36:45.520 --> 00:36:46.320
Sa likod namin.

00:36:46.400 --> 00:36:47.080
Pumunta, pumunta!

00:36:47.080 --> 00:36:47.640
Pumunta!

00:36:50.920 --> 00:36:52.280
Oo, tama iyan.

00:36:52.280 --> 00:36:53.680
Halos magpumiglas ako sa puwet.

00:36:57.200 --> 00:36:58.480
Tara na. Diretso lang.

00:37:04.000 --> 00:37:05.560
Bakit biglang naging malabo?

00:37:05.680 --> 00:37:07.440
Oo, kakaibang panahon para sa hamog.

00:37:07.480 --> 00:37:09.240
Maayos naman ang lahat ngayon lang.

00:37:09.920 --> 00:37:11.560
Saang daan tayo pupunta ngayon?

00:37:11.680 --> 00:37:12.560
Kasalanan ko.

00:37:12.840 --> 00:37:13.680
Akala ko

00:37:13.680 --> 00:37:15.440
Nakahanap ako ng shortcut.

00:37:15.520 --> 00:37:17.080
Hindi inaasahan na mawawala.

00:37:19.280 --> 00:37:19.960
Mayroong

00:37:20.880 --> 00:37:22.480
wala talagang signal dito.

00:37:22.600 --> 00:37:23.320
Siguro ang mga satellite

00:37:23.320 --> 00:37:24.880
huwag mo kaming saklawin dito.

00:37:25.600 --> 00:37:25.840
Noong kami ay

00:37:25.840 --> 00:37:27.560
nagmamaneho dito,

00:37:27.560 --> 00:37:28.440
ang GPS ay naroon na

00:37:28.440 --> 00:37:29.320
pagbibigay ng maling direksyon.

00:37:29.320 --> 00:37:30.520
Hindi ba't sinabi mo

00:37:30.520 --> 00:37:31.640
Nakapunta ka na ba rito dati?

00:37:31.920 --> 00:37:33.240
Malapit na ako,

00:37:33.400 --> 00:37:34.360
hindi eksakto rito.

00:37:35.200 --> 00:37:35.920
Aba...

00:37:36.920 --> 00:37:37.360
Sinta.

00:37:37.360 --> 00:37:38.840
Pasensya na po.

00:37:38.880 --> 00:37:40.440
Hindi maganda ang kamay ko para sa

00:37:40.440 --> 00:37:41.440
pagpipiloto.

00:37:43.800 --> 00:37:44.800
Ang buong bagay tungkol sa direksyon,

00:37:44.800 --> 00:37:46.640
simula ngayon,

00:37:47.160 --> 00:37:48.480
Ibinibigay ko na ito sa iyo.

00:37:49.280 --> 00:37:50.800
Magpepedal na lang ako sa likod.

00:37:51.560 --> 00:37:53.120
Kung saan mo sinasabi, doon ako pupunta.

00:37:53.520 --> 00:37:54.320
Okay?

00:37:56.560 --> 00:37:57.160
Sige.

00:37:58.120 --> 00:37:59.040
Kaya ngayon, dapat ba nating

00:37:59.040 --> 00:38:00.200
magpahinga ka rito,

00:38:00.360 --> 00:38:01.640
hintayin mong mawala ang hamog?

00:38:01.640 --> 00:38:02.480
O ano?

00:38:02.680 --> 00:38:03.480
Ang iyong tawag.

00:38:03.680 --> 00:38:04.560
Kahit ano pa ang sabihin mo,

00:38:04.560 --> 00:38:05.520
ginagawa namin.

00:38:06.680 --> 00:38:07.480
Ang tawag ko?

00:38:08.760 --> 00:38:10.880
Pagkatapos ay pupunta tayo

00:38:11.600 --> 00:38:12.240
dito!

00:38:12.880 --> 00:38:14.000
- Tara na.
- Tara na.

00:38:15.120 --> 00:38:15.720
Tara na.

00:38:18.240 --> 00:38:19.800
Huwag mong patulan 'yan.

00:38:22.760 --> 00:38:23.920
Baliktarin ko!

00:38:24.120 --> 00:38:25.520
Baliktarin! Baliktarin!

00:38:25.520 --> 00:38:27.560
Tara na!

00:38:28.840 --> 00:38:29.640
Ge Kaiyang,

00:38:30.600 --> 00:38:31.280
tandaan ang panahong iyon

00:38:31.280 --> 00:38:32.880
pumunta tayo para makita ang pagsikat ng araw?

00:38:33.960 --> 00:38:36.160
Sabi ko buhay,

00:38:36.600 --> 00:38:37.640
kapag lumingon ka pabalik,

00:38:37.640 --> 00:38:38.360
ay talagang

00:38:38.360 --> 00:38:39.520
mga ilang sandali.

00:38:40.560 --> 00:38:41.400
Siyempre naaalala ko.

00:38:42.600 --> 00:38:43.200
Ngayon sa tingin ko

00:38:43.200 --> 00:38:44.360
Mas may katuturan ito kaysa dati.

00:38:44.360 --> 00:38:45.920
Ilang taon ka na,

00:38:46.120 --> 00:38:47.680
nagiging puro pilosopo?

00:38:47.960 --> 00:38:49.200
Sentimental lang ang pakiramdam.

00:38:50.000 --> 00:38:51.320
Tingnan mo itong ilog,

00:38:52.040 --> 00:38:53.080
ito ay dumadaloy nang walang tigil.

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:54.800
Nakapasa na tayo

00:38:54.800 --> 00:38:55.800
napakaraming tinidor,

00:38:56.760 --> 00:38:58.160
napakaraming eksena ang napanood,

00:38:59.680 --> 00:39:00.640
sumalubong sa makapal na hamog,

00:39:01.080 --> 00:39:02.160
kahit tumama sa mga bato.

00:39:03.120 --> 00:39:04.320
Pero iyon ang bumubuo

00:39:04.320 --> 00:39:05.320
ang ating paglalakbay,

00:39:05.960 --> 00:39:06.400
tama?

00:39:12.720 --> 00:39:13.360
Totoo.

00:39:19.640 --> 00:39:20.400
Lu Xinying.

00:39:20.400 --> 00:39:22.200
Ang tagal ko nang naghihintay.

00:39:22.920 --> 00:39:24.640
Literal na natapos ko ang isang libro.

00:39:25.360 --> 00:39:26.320
Masyadong mabagal.

00:39:26.320 --> 00:39:28.360
Hindi naman ganoon kasama.

00:39:28.960 --> 00:39:30.320
Hindi ba't sinabi mo

00:39:30.840 --> 00:39:32.240
isang baluktot na puno

00:39:32.240 --> 00:39:33.160
ay ang finish line?

00:39:33.160 --> 00:39:33.880
Nasaan ito?

00:39:34.320 --> 00:39:35.040
Kita mo?

00:39:35.400 --> 00:39:36.360
Sinabi ko na sa'yo.

00:39:36.880 --> 00:39:38.280
Mukhang lahat tayo ay sumasang-ayon.

00:39:38.400 --> 00:39:39.600
Sa tingin ko, si Zhang Ran.

00:39:39.600 --> 00:39:40.680
nilinaw ito.

00:39:41.040 --> 00:39:41.800
Alam mo,

00:39:42.400 --> 00:39:44.200
kahit anong baluktot na puno

00:39:44.200 --> 00:39:44.920
sa tingin mo ay

00:39:44.920 --> 00:39:45.840
ang iyong linya ng pagtatapos,

00:39:45.840 --> 00:39:47.200
ayan na.

00:39:47.200 --> 00:39:47.760
Para sa akin,

00:39:47.760 --> 00:39:48.240
ito na ang isa

00:39:48.240 --> 00:39:49.440
nakita namin noong kami

00:39:49.440 --> 00:39:50.240
unang pag-alis.

00:39:50.240 --> 00:39:51.600
Matagal ko nang natapos.

00:39:51.760 --> 00:39:52.480
Bakit hindi na lang sabihin ang puno

00:39:52.480 --> 00:39:53.480
sa labas ng iyong pinto

00:39:53.480 --> 00:39:54.680
ay ang finish line?

00:39:56.320 --> 00:39:56.960
Siya nga pala, Zhang Ran,

00:39:56.960 --> 00:39:58.320
Matagal ko nang gustong sabihin sa'yo.

00:39:58.320 --> 00:39:59.080
Oo?

00:40:00.680 --> 00:40:03.320
Ha! / Ha!

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:05.160
Kukunin kita!

00:40:05.160 --> 00:40:06.160
Hoy,

00:40:06.920 --> 00:40:08.200
Nakahabol na ako!

00:40:08.960 --> 00:40:12.040
Lagpasan mo ang sarili mong baluktot na puno.

00:40:12.280 --> 00:40:14.200
Baliw si Li Daoqi.

00:40:15.280 --> 00:40:16.800
Oo! Unang pwesto!

00:40:16.880 --> 00:40:17.840
Hindi pwede, hindi ako pwedeng magpahuli.

00:40:17.840 --> 00:40:18.840
Tatamaan ako sa puno.

00:40:19.640 --> 00:40:22.280
Lagpasan mo ang baluktot na puno!

00:40:23.400 --> 00:40:24.320
Pumunta! Pumunta!

00:40:24.880 --> 00:40:26.120
Unang pwesto!

00:40:26.120 --> 00:40:27.760
Maling paraan!

